title: 820-4924-A dead
message:

title: 820-4924-A dead
message:

Check diode mode between R7120/50.
If short, change Q7130.

title: 820-4924-A dead
message:
0.028 is close to expected value; should be 20 ohm.
However, R7120/21 can't have 10K each one; 10 ohm is other thing.
Please, post accurate information.

Change Q7180 and test again with original charger.
